summary: Kira is manipulating a closeted boy because she likes him. She’s using TJ to hurt Buffy and Cyrus. She’s rude, selfish, and...
body:
Kira is manipulating a closeted boy because she likes him. She’s using TJ to hurt Buffy and Cyrus. She’s rude, selfish, and doesn’t care who she has to hurt as long as she gets her way. There’s so many reasons to hate her. Another reason to hate her is because of TJ and Cyrus. She saw them together and she automatically assumed they were gay. It may have been obvious but that’s still a big assumption. Her personality is a great reason to call her horrible. But there’s one thing that makes me hate her with my whole fucking being.

She took away their happiness and never gave it back.
